```plantuml
@startuml TestHaters_ctflow

actor User
participant "VS Code" as VSCode
participant "React Webview UI" as Webview
participant "CtFlowEditorProvider" as Editor
participant "Compiler" as Compiler
participant "Cypress" as Cypress

User -> VSCode: Opens CTFLOW extension
VSCode -> Editor: Registers CtFlowEditorProvider
Editor -> Webview: Creates React Webview UI
Webview -> User: Displays drag-and-drop interface

loop Test Creation
    User -> Webview: Drags and drops nodes
    Webview -> Editor: Updates flow state
    Editor -> Webview: Persists to .ctflow file
end

User -> Webview: Clicks "Compile" button
Webview -> Compiler: Sends flow graph
Compiler -> Compiler: Converts to Cypress code
Compiler -> Cypress: Generates test files
Cypress -> Cypress: Executes tests
Cypress -> Webview: Returns test results
Webview -> User: Displays test results

@enduml
```